CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

June 18, 2013

[Cite as 06/18/2013 Case Announcements, 2013-0hio-2503.]

DISCIPLINARY CASES

2011-1681. Cleveland Metro. Bar Assn. v. Davie.

This cause came on for further consideration upon the filing of a motion to appear by written and sworn testimony and a motion to withdraw counsel of record by respondent, Michael Davie.

Upon consideration thereof, it is ordered by the court that respondent’s motion to appear by written and sworn testimony is denied as moot. The court further orders that respondent’s motion to withdraw counsel of record is granted.
